{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shipwrecked on a mysterious island, the Mariner must harness its power to return home. Unravel the island's past in this tight 3D platformer, find all the inscriptions, and piece together the story of a bygone civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A precision platformer:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse the various areas of the island and overcome the challenges contained in the portals to unlock new powers, in this 3D platformer that offers hard levels and a continuous challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A lore to discover:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reconstruct the history of the island and its previous inhabitants by reading and collecting damaged inscriptions and diaries of those who came before, and unravel the mysteries of the game world and the Mariner himself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A traveling companion:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Share your journey with the mysterious Keeper of the island, the only remaining inhabitant, who will confide in you, reflecting on the island and giving you directions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Sanctuaries:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each area of the island is characterized by a different Sanctuary. Reach the top and face the challenges in sequence, proceeding linearly based on the powers unlocked.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376630/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733832958","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376630/page.bg.jpg?t=1733832958","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376630/e952e6169e1b3ffecb9b02fb33ab6146c03425c8/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733832958","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto